{"tid":1580574,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"大家print出尼去投注站貼","createTime":"2019-09-19T06:43:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-19T09:57:48.000Z","uid":75277,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3404870e0e2e55507662234988dc9697237075c3","tid":1580574,"uid":75277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T06:43:12.000Z","msg":"大家print出尼去投注站貼<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NPDv1WX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNPDv1WX.jpg&h=e425182d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9e6181a82efb108317b31d144433bf3dc58d6950","tid":1580574,"uid":269515,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T06:49:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nqctagq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnqctagq.png&h=7fed4eca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我朋友係福建人<br />\n<br />\n佢話何生琴日係街比馬迷鬧係過街老鼠<br />\n<br />\n新聞訪問阿叔又係咁鬧何生<br />\n<br />\n何生依家準備吹大雞要打馬迷 開始召集福建幫<br />\n<br />\n仲話呢排一見到有人拎馬經就話要打<br />\n<br />\n佢地今次唔係針對果班暴徒曱甴<br />\n<br />\n係針對我地班馬迷 各位黎緊跑馬既馬迷要小心！<br />\n<br />\n好人一生平安"},{"pid":"bac6ab33bc2e61870688844f6d2c5e3c058fd5e3","tid":1580574,"uid":75277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T07:14:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09b8e6bab2ea02023d625f930aac432aa83c0d1f","tid":1580574,"uid":64810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T07:14:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6f93ddc5ba5096916cd194c96762e9db8807ad4","tid":1580574,"uid":227405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T07:15:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ec2a3d4394901224cbaa9dca5f258dce08c83306","tid":1580574,"uid":256